Uh, take some ribbon, yes...ooh, uh uh, not there...(nervous) ooh, yes...

129
00:07:42,077 --> 00:07:45,079
Uh, tuck it in over there, uh, but be 
 careful not to...
(Twilight bending and cracking wood)

130
