Well, you sure have a lot of work ahead of you.

154
00:08:57,031 --> 00:08:59,026
There's quite a few lakes in Ponyville.

155
00:08:59,026 --> 00:09:00,093
Pinkie Pie: (scoffs) Tell me about it.

156
00:09:00,932 --> 00:09:03,016
Hey, Twilight! Wanna help me out?

157
00:09:03,161 --> 00:09:04,037
Twilight: Would I?!

158
00:09:04,369 --> 00:09:08,050
Pinkie Pie: Come on. Put on those skates over 
 there. I bet you'll be a natural, too.

159
00:09:08,502 --> 00:09:09,057
Twilight: Okay.

160
