(Twilight's legs wobbling)
Pinkie Pie: WHEEEE!

161
00:09:12,821 --> 00:09:15,075
Twilight: (nervously) Uh...maybe on second thought... (thud)
(Pinkie Pie laughing and giggling in background)

162
