 wake up every animal before spring comes.

204
00:11:23,085 --> 00:11:25,004
Twilight: Well, I'll help, Fluttershy.

205
00:11:25,035 --> 00:11:28,094
Fluttershy: You will? Oh, that would be wonderful.

206
00:11:28,936 --> 00:11:32,051
